<i>and the way of grace.</i>

02:15.135 --> 02:17.603
<i>You have to choose
which one you'll follow.</i>

02:30.416 --> 02:32.611
<i>Grace doesn't try to please itself.</i>

02:35.488 --> 02:39.788
<i>Accepts being slighted,
forgotten, disliked.</i>

02:43.997 --> 02:46.966
<i>Accepts insults and injuries.</i>

02:58.478 --> 02:59.945
Ooh!

03:05.518 --> 03:08.612
<i>Nature only wants to please itself.</i>

03:08.721 --> 03:12.851
- Bless, O Lord, this food to our use-
- <i>Get others to please it too.</i>

03:12.959 --> 03:14.586
...your loving and faithful service.

03:14.694 --> 03:16.423
<i>Likes to lord it over them.</i>

03:16.529 --> 03:18.429
<i>Bless these boys.</i>

03:18.531 --> 03:20.999
<i>To have its own way.</i>

03:25.471 --> 03:28.031
<i>It finds reasons to be unhappy...</i>

03:28.141 --> 03:31.406
<i>when all the world
is shining around it...</i>

03:32.478 --> 03:35.276
<i>when love is smiling
through all things.</i>

03:50.597 --> 03:54.328
<i>They taught us that no one
who loves the way of grace...</i>

03:54.434 --> 03:57.096
<i>ever comes to a bad end.</i>

04:04.677 --> 04:06.838
<i>I will be true to you.</i>

04:08.848 --> 04:10.179
<i>Whatever comes.</i>

05:00.366 --> 05:01.663
Oh, God!

06:31.557 --> 06:33.525
<i>My son.</i>

06:41.467 --> 06:44.834
I just want to die...

06:44.937 --> 06:46.905
<i>to be with him.</i>

07:27.113 --> 07:30.048
<i>He's in God's hands now.</i>

07:35.822 --> 07:38.689
He was in God's hands the whole time.

07:41.461 --> 07:43.326
<i>Wasn't he?</i>

07:47.467 --> 07:49.367
<i>My hope.</i>

07:54.140 --> 07:55.767
<i>My God.</i>

08:02.381 --> 08:04.474
<i>"I shall fear no evil-</i>

08:06.152 --> 08:08.552
<i>fear no evil,
for you are with me. "</i>

08:08.654 --> 08:10.588
<i>What did you gain?</i>

08:10.690 --> 08:12.954
<i>"Be not far from me,
for trouble is near."</i>

08:13.059 --> 08:15.254
Okay, go on now.
We're all right.

08:18.197 --> 08:20.290
We're all right.

08:29.141 --> 08:31.234
Thank you. Thank you.

08:36.182 --> 08:40.174
Sure, you have your memories of him, and, uh-

08:40.285 --> 08:42.379
you're gonna have to be strong now and-

08:45.658 --> 08:48.422
I know the pain will-

08:48.528 --> 08:50.393
It will pass in time, you know?

08:50.496 --> 08:53.158
It might seem... hard, my saying that...

08:53.266 --> 08:54.790
but it's true.

08:54.901 --> 08:56.869
