08:59.505 --> 09:01.405
Life goes on.

09:03.409 --> 09:05.309
People pass along.

09:07.079 --> 09:09.445
Nothing stays the same.

09:12.652 --> 09:15.018
You've still got the other two.

09:21.193 --> 09:23.718
The Lord gives, and the Lord takes away...

09:23.829 --> 09:25.922
and...

09:26.032 --> 09:28.000
that's the way he is.

09:34.173 --> 09:36.437
He sends flies to wounds...

09:36.542 --> 09:38.669
that he should heal.

09:55.728 --> 09:58.856
<i>I never got a chance
to tell him how sorry I was.</i>

10:05.271 --> 10:07.171
One night he...

10:09.141 --> 10:12.838
punched him- himself in the face
for no reason.

10:20.186 --> 10:22.154
