10:46.946 --> 10:48.573
My shame.

10:53.552 --> 10:56.316
That poor boy.

10:56.422 --> 10:58.322
That poor boy.

11:27.953 --> 11:30.080
<i>How did you come to me?</i>

11:37.029 --> 11:39.224
<i>In what shape?</i>

11:43.703 --> 11:45.432
<i>What disguise?</i>

