01:06:03.726 --> 01:06:05.751
Left. Left.

01:06:05.861 --> 01:06:07.590
Right. Right.

01:06:07.696 --> 01:06:11.154
Left. Harder. Harder. Harder!

01:06:11.267 --> 01:06:13.428
Come on, hit me. Hit me.

01:06:13.536 --> 01:06:16.198
Come on, Son. Hit it.
Give me something.

01:06:16.305 --> 01:06:18.273
Show me what you got.

01:06:19.875 --> 01:06:21.866
Come on. Go on.

01:06:27.616 --> 01:06:29.243
One meal.

01:06:44.500 --> 01:06:46.400
Leave the table.

01:06:52.308 --> 01:06:53.935
You too?

01:06:55.611 --> 01:06:57.602
- You gonna continue to defy me?
- No, sir.

01:06:57.713 --> 01:07:00.739
You interrupted me.
I wasn't done yet.

01:07:03.786 --> 01:07:05.549
Am I finished?

01:07:06.589 --> 01:07:08.216
May I?

01:07:09.391 --> 01:07:12.053
Thank you, Your Majesty.

01:08:08.584 --> 01:08:10.711
<i>Makes up stories.</i>

01:08:13.822 --> 01:08:15.722
<i>Original words.</i>

01:08:23.799 --> 01:08:26.859
<i>He says,
"Don't put your elbows on the table."</i>

01:08:26.969 --> 01:08:28.765
Are you ready?

01:08:28.871 --> 01:08:30.770
<i>He does.</i>

01:08:34.276 --> 01:08:36.176
<i>Insults people.</i>

01:08:37.645 --> 01:08:39.273
<i>Doesn't care.</i>

01:08:39.381 --> 01:08:41.679
<i>I remember when you were born.</i>

01:08:46.822 --> 01:08:48.790
They wouldn't let me come home.

01:08:50.559 --> 01:08:53.995
The navy said an officer must be present
for the laying of the keel...

01:08:54.095 --> 01:08:58.055
but... not at the launching.

01:09:42.144 --> 01:09:44.374
The next word is "volcano."

01:09:54.957 --> 01:09:56.948
The next word is "socket."

01:10:03.032 --> 01:10:06.832
Please pass your answers to each other.
We're gonna grade each other's papers now.

01:10:12.674 --> 01:10:14.574
No interruptions, please.

01:10:16.378 --> 01:10:18.846
Come on. Get your pencil out.

01:10:23.819 --> 01:10:26.287
After logs go to the paper mill-

01:11:39.495 --> 01:11:43.090
Taylor! Taylor, sweetheart!

01:11:43.198 --> 01:11:45.496
Honey! Honey!

01:11:52.407 --> 01:11:53.806
Let me go!

01:13:13.855 --> 01:13:15.652
<i>Was he bad?</i>

01:13:25.267 --> 01:13:27.735
Will you die too?

01:13:30.572 --> 01:13:33.063
<i>You're not that old yet, Mom.</i>

01:13:50.792 --> 01:13:52.589
<i>Where were you?</i>

01:14:04.806 --> 01:14:06.706
<i>You let a boy die.</i>

01:14:13.715 --> 01:14:16.183
<i>You'll let anything happen.</i>

01:14:29.464 --> 01:14:30.988
I can't see!

01:14:31.099 --> 01:14:32.896
I can't see!

01:14:36.605 --> 01:14:38.505
<i>Why should I be good...</i>

01:14:42.544 --> 01:14:45.172
<i>if you aren't?</i>

01:15:34.129 --> 01:15:35.756
Thank you.

01:15:50.479 --> 01:15:53.039
Too close.

01:15:53.148 --> 01:15:55.116
Edges.

01:15:55.217 --> 01:15:57.708
Why's this bare here, hmm?

01:15:57.819 --> 01:16:01.118
- Grass won't grow under the trees.
- Does at the Kimballs'.

01:16:01.223 --> 01:16:04.317
- They have a yardman.
- They have money.

01:16:04.426 --> 01:16:06.394
Course, he inherited it.

01:16:08.430 --> 01:16:11.831
I don't want to hear one more word out of you,
not till this is finished.

01:16:23.645 --> 01:16:25.203
Hmm?

01:16:29.284 --> 01:16:30.842
Hmm?

01:16:52.741 --> 01:16:54.368
Cropping that too close.

01:16:54.476 --> 01:16:56.137
You're gonna have to keep that watered.

01:17:03.585 --> 01:17:05.485
Not high enough.

01:17:23.772 --> 01:17:25.637
Toscanini...

01:17:25.740 --> 01:17:27.935
once recorded a piece 65 times.

01:17:28.043 --> 01:17:30.443
You know what he said when he finished?

01:17:30.545 --> 01:17:32.570
"It could be better."

01:17:34.082 --> 01:17:35.709
Think about it.

01:17:38.286 --> 01:17:40.754
Twenty-seven patents your father has.

01:17:42.324 --> 01:17:45.225
<i>It means ownership.
Ownership of ideas.</i>

01:17:46.828 --> 01:17:49.092
<i>You gotta sew 'em up.
Get 'em by the nuts-</i>

01:17:49.197 --> 01:17:51.722
- We'll get 'em next time.
- <i>pardon my French.</i>

01:17:51.833 --> 01:17:53.528
<i>We'll be rich.</i>

01:17:56.671 --> 01:17:59.139
<i>You make yourself what you are.</i>

01:18:02.744 --> 01:18:05.542
<i>You have control of your own destiny.</i>

01:18:08.650 --> 01:18:10.618
<i>You can't say, "I can't."</i>

01:18:11.786 --> 01:18:13.686
<i>You say, "I'm having trouble.</i>

01:18:14.956 --> 01:18:16.685
I'm not done yet."

01:18:18.493 --> 01:18:20.927
<i>You can't say, "I can't."</i>

01:18:54.829 --> 01:18:57.024
<i>Why does he hurt us?</i>

01:18:59.367 --> 01:19:00.994
<i>Our father.</i>

01:19:06.975 --> 01:19:08.806
Come on, Dix. Come on!

01:19:08.910 --> 01:19:10.241
Ah, yeah. Get it! Get it!

01:19:24.526 --> 01:19:26.551
Give your father a kiss.

01:20:05.800 --> 01:20:07.358
<i>He lies.</i>

01:20:11.072 --> 01:20:13.370
- <i>Pretends.</i>
- Can you do something for me?

01:20:13.475 --> 01:20:15.909
You promise you'll do it
without having to ask what it is?

01:20:16.011 --> 01:20:18.639
Just have the confidence that
what your father asks of you is right?

01:20:18.747 --> 01:20:20.510
Yes, sir.

01:20:20.615 --> 01:20:25.314
For the next half hour, will you not speak
unless you have something important to say?

01:20:30.759 --> 01:20:33.227
What'd you do today,
my fine feathered friend?

01:20:35.096 --> 01:20:39.465
Sit on the front two inches of your chair.
Better for your posture.

01:20:39.567 --> 01:20:41.535
I read that in the paper.

01:20:44.673 --> 01:20:48.040
Did you actually buy this
from Mr. Ledbetter?

01:20:48.143 --> 01:20:50.771
Don't explain.
Just nod- yes or no.

01:20:52.047 --> 01:20:53.674
- Hmm?
- No.

01:20:56.217 --> 01:20:57.514
Be quiet.

01:21:00.555 --> 01:21:02.523
What did you say?

01:21:05.326 --> 01:21:06.953
Please.

01:21:07.062 --> 01:21:08.689
- Leave him alone!
- Come here!

01:21:08.797 --> 01:21:10.958
Honey!

01:21:11.066 --> 01:21:14.524
Leave him alone!

01:21:17.872 --> 01:21:20.238
Come here! Get back. Come here.

01:21:24.579 --> 01:21:26.479
Get up there!

01:22:22.704 --> 01:22:24.433
You turned my own kids against me.

01:22:26.141 --> 01:22:28.075
You undermine everything I do.

01:22:37.352 --> 01:22:38.944
- How do you like-
- Stop-

01:22:39.788 --> 01:22:41.085
Stop it.

01:22:41.189 --> 01:22:44.317
Stop it! Stop. Stop it.

01:22:48.429 --> 01:22:49.760
Stop it.

01:22:52.700 --> 01:22:54.167
Stop it.

01:22:59.707 --> 01:23:01.834
Stop. Stop.

01:25:00.962 --> 01:25:02.827
Where's Dad?

01:25:02.931 --> 01:25:04.990
He's gone on a trip.

01:25:14.242 --> 01:25:16.142
Whoo!

01:25:16.711 --> 01:25:18.178
Whoo!

01:25:24.519 --> 01:25:25.986
No!

01:25:35.663 --> 01:25:37.528
Open the door!

01:25:48.676 --> 01:25:50.143
- Get her!
- No!

01:25:50.244 --> 01:25:51.734
<i>Help each other.</i>

01:25:53.081 --> 01:25:56.016
Do not slam that screen door!

01:25:57.819 --> 01:26:00.617
<i>Love everyone.</i>

01:26:02.623 --> 01:26:04.523
<i>Every leaf.</i>

01:26:06.194 --> 01:26:08.719
<i>Every ray of light.</i>

01:26:16.304 --> 01:26:18.169
<i>Forgive.</i>

01:26:45.666 --> 01:26:47.566
This is my house!

01:26:47.668 --> 01:26:49.397
You're allowed to live here!

01:26:49.504 --> 01:26:51.631
You are allowed to live here!

01:26:53.341 --> 01:26:55.138
Get out of my way!

01:26:55.243 --> 01:26:57.006
No!

01:26:57.111 --> 01:26:58.908
Shut up!

01:27:13.327 --> 01:27:16.262
I got it, I got it, I got it!

01:27:53.734 --> 01:27:56.362
- Boom! Boom! Boom, boom!
- Boom, boom!

01:27:56.471 --> 01:27:58.132
- Watch out!
- Watch out!

01:27:58.239 --> 01:28:00.605
Go!

01:28:06.781 --> 01:28:09.443
One, two, three!

01:28:17.658 --> 01:28:19.319
I say let's bust 'em.

01:28:32.273 --> 01:28:33.831
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

01:28:43.417 --> 01:28:44.611
Yeah!

01:28:45.753 --> 01:28:47.015
We found a frog!

01:28:48.656 --> 01:28:50.419
Let's go set it off with a skyrocket!

01:28:50.525 --> 01:28:52.015
He's getting away!

01:28:53.961 --> 01:28:55.895
Get back! Get back!

01:29:03.104 --> 01:29:04.935
Did it go to the moon?

01:29:07.775 --> 01:29:09.333
Where is he?

01:29:09.443 --> 01:29:11.070
Here he is.

01:29:13.047 --> 01:29:15.072
It was an experiment!

01:29:19.287 --> 01:29:20.584
<i>Liar.</i>

01:29:22.757 --> 01:29:24.554
Never do it again.

01:29:25.626 --> 01:29:27.093
Promise?

01:29:30.565 --> 01:29:32.897
You gonna tell Dad?

01:29:33.000 --> 01:29:36.094
<i>They're just trying to scare you.</i>

01:29:38.806 --> 01:29:40.535
Keep you ignorant.

01:29:44.779 --> 01:29:46.406
<i>Things you got to learn.</i>

01:29:50.585 --> 01:29:52.678
<i>How can we know stuff
until we look?</i>

01:30:11.205 --> 01:30:14.504
They say you can't try stuff?
They do.

01:30:18.779 --> 01:30:20.337
What do you need to be afraid of?

01:30:24.118 --> 01:30:25.710
You're afraid.

01:30:27.421 --> 01:30:28.615
I see it.

01:30:28.723 --> 01:30:31.283
Right here! Right here!

01:35:55.950 --> 01:35:58.111
I can't talk to you.

01:36:07.227 --> 01:36:09.559
Don't look at me.

01:36:57.211 --> 01:36:58.678
<i>What have I started?</i>

01:37:02.783 --> 01:37:04.546
<i>What have I done?</i>

01:37:35.182 --> 01:37:36.877
Stick it in there.

01:38:16.356 --> 01:38:17.983
I trust you.

01:38:33.574 --> 01:38:35.906
- <i>You tired?</i>
- <i>No!</i>

01:38:36.009 --> 01:38:38.375
I never get tired!

01:38:38.479 --> 01:38:40.879
- Did this morning.
- No, I was just pretending.

01:38:41.915 --> 01:38:44.042
- Gonna call me a liar?
- No.

01:38:44.151 --> 01:38:46.051
I don't want to fight.

01:38:46.153 --> 01:38:48.212
Afraid to?

01:38:48.322 --> 01:38:50.119
No, I just don't wanna.

01:38:51.959 --> 01:38:54.655
If I was to say you're scared,
would you call me a liar?

01:38:54.762 --> 01:38:55.854
No.

01:38:57.131 --> 01:38:59.099
<i>Then you're scared, aren't you?</i>

01:39:08.342 --> 01:39:10.173
Aha!

01:39:10.277 --> 01:39:11.904
Quit it.

01:39:14.414 --> 01:39:15.745
Come here.

01:39:59.927 --> 01:40:01.554
Come here!

01:40:04.164 --> 01:40:05.688
No!

01:40:08.769 --> 01:40:11.169
I'm not gonna do everything
you tell me to.

01:40:12.472 --> 01:40:14.702
I'm gonna do what I want.

01:40:18.245 --> 01:40:20.907
What do you know?
You let him run all over you.

01:41:11.665 --> 01:41:13.599
<i>How do I get back...</i>

01:41:19.106 --> 01:41:20.698
<i>where they are?</i>

01:41:43.864 --> 01:41:45.832
- How are you, Son?
- Good.

01:41:55.542 --> 01:41:58.443
This one's heavy.
You're gonna need two hands for that one.

01:42:05.786 --> 01:42:07.253
Whoa.

01:42:08.288 --> 01:42:10.449
Careful now. You know what that-

01:42:10.557 --> 01:42:12.218
- Chinese?
- Know what that- That's Chinese.

01:42:12.326 --> 01:42:14.294
That's very good. Yes, it is.

01:42:15.996 --> 01:42:18.863
Your father went all around the world,
all the way to China.

01:42:18.966 --> 01:42:20.831
That's Pan Am airlines.

01:42:20.934 --> 01:42:22.799
That's what your father flew on.

01:42:22.903 --> 01:42:25.838
The entire bathrooms are stainless steel,
even the washbasin.

01:42:25.939 --> 01:42:29.238
I feel confident the deal's going through.

01:42:29.343 --> 01:42:32.176
If not, they can forget it.
I'll tell them all to go to hell.

01:42:32.279 --> 01:42:34.372
- That's from Germany.
- How do you use them?

01:42:34.481 --> 01:42:35.880
See that?

01:42:39.086 --> 01:42:40.917
Put that down, Son.

01:42:41.021 --> 01:42:43.353
Can Cayler come over?

01:42:43.457 --> 01:42:45.857
Is your family not good enough for you?

01:42:52.032 --> 01:42:55.934
Hope it's not gonna take
as long as last time.

01:42:56.036 --> 01:42:57.503
Al dente.

01:43:00.874 --> 01:43:03.206
Subjective point of view.
You know the difference?

01:43:03.310 --> 01:43:06.370
"Subjective" means it comes from your mind.
Can't be proven by other people.

01:43:06.480 --> 01:43:08.539
Mwah.

01:43:08.648 --> 01:43:10.115
So- Here you go.

01:43:10.217 --> 01:43:11.912
Mm, mm, oop, oop, oop.

01:43:14.821 --> 01:43:16.982
- Good to see you again.
- Okay.

01:43:17.090 --> 01:43:19.149
Let's go, boys.

01:43:19.259 --> 01:43:20.556
Come on.

01:43:21.895 --> 01:43:23.863
There are things you can't do?

01:43:23.964 --> 01:43:25.898
Well, there are things
I can't do either.

01:43:27.501 --> 01:43:29.628
You are not to call me "Dad."
You will call me "Father."

01:43:29.736 --> 01:43:31.397
- But-
- But- Don't interrupt!

01:43:31.505 --> 01:43:33.405
- But you do.
- Don't interrupt!

01:43:39.446 --> 01:43:40.913
It's your house.

01:43:41.014 --> 01:43:43.209
You can kick me out
whenever you want to.

01:43:48.855 --> 01:43:50.880
You'd like to kill me.

01:44:09.976 --> 01:44:11.773
- No-
- <i>Dad.</i>

01:44:16.283 --> 01:44:18.274
Why was he born?

01:45:43.837 --> 01:45:46.305
<i>Please, God, kill him.</i>

01:45:50.677 --> 01:45:52.668
<i>Let him die.</i>

01:45:57.317 --> 01:45:59.080
<i>Get him out of here.</i>

01:46:20.840 --> 01:46:22.740
She only loves me!

01:46:34.387 --> 01:46:38.346
<i>Defend, O Lord, this thy child
with thy heavenly grace...</i>

01:46:38.458 --> 01:46:41.450
that he may continue thine forever...

01:46:41.561 --> 01:46:45.429
and daily increase
in thy holy spirit more and more...

01:46:45.532 --> 01:46:49.491
until he come unto thy everlasting kingdom.

01:46:49.603 --> 01:46:50.900
<i>Amen.</i>

01:47:31.811 --> 01:47:33.438
I see something.

01:48:24.431 --> 01:48:26.092
Put your finger over it.

01:48:28.301 --> 01:48:29.598
Like that.

01:48:31.838 --> 01:48:33.066
Come on.

01:49:30.497 --> 01:49:33.193
<i>What I want to do, I can't do.</i>

01:49:38.905 --> 01:49:40.770
<i>I do what I hate.</i>

01:50:42.202 --> 01:50:43.897
You can hit me if you want.

01:51:02.021 --> 01:51:03.352
I'm sorry.

01:51:06.893 --> 01:51:08.690
You're my brother.

01:51:52.839 --> 01:51:54.966
<i>What was it you showed me?</i>

01:52:04.117 --> 01:52:06.984
<i>I didn't know how to name you then.</i>

01:52:11.491 --> 01:52:13.550
<i>But I see it was you.</i>

01:52:19.365 --> 01:52:21.458
<i>Always you were calling me.</i>

01:54:11.144 --> 01:54:14.443
<i>I wanted to be loved
because I was great.</i>

01:54:16.949 --> 01:54:18.940
<i>A big man.</i>

01:54:21.521 --> 01:54:22.988
<i>I'm nothin'.</i>

01:54:26.893 --> 01:54:29.794
<i>Look... at the glory around us.</i>

01:54:32.999 --> 01:54:35.467
<i>Trees and birds.</i>

01:54:39.005 --> 01:54:40.529
<i>I lived in shame.</i>

01:54:44.377 --> 01:54:47.437
<i>I dishonored it all
and didn't notice the glory.</i>

01:54:53.519 --> 01:54:55.316
<i>I'm a foolish man.</i>

01:55:00.526 --> 01:55:02.494
They're closing the plant.

01:55:06.566 --> 01:55:09.057
They gave me a choice.

01:55:11.471 --> 01:55:13.234
No job...

01:55:16.042 --> 01:55:19.341
or a transfer to a job nobody wants.

01:55:28.321 --> 01:55:29.982
<i>Father.</i>

01:55:32.358 --> 01:55:35.225
<i>I never missed a day of work.</i>

01:55:35.328 --> 01:55:37.296
<i>Mother.</i>

01:55:37.396 --> 01:55:39.956
<i>I tithed every Sunday.</i>

01:55:43.569 --> 01:55:46.561
<i>Always you wrestle inside me.</i>

01:55:51.577 --> 01:55:53.545
<i>Always you will.</i>

01:55:54.547 --> 01:55:59.780
You know, Jack,
all I ever wanted for you was...

01:55:59.886 --> 01:56:02.684
to make you strong and-

01:56:02.789 --> 01:56:04.848
and grow up and be your own boss.

01:56:08.294 --> 01:56:10.421
Maybe I've been tough on you.

01:56:12.331 --> 01:56:14.356
I'm not proud of that.

01:56:16.669 --> 01:56:18.660
I'm as bad as you are.

01:56:21.240 --> 01:56:23.868
I'm more like you than her.

01:56:32.485 --> 01:56:35.716
You boys are about all I've done in life.
Otherwise I've drawn zilch.

01:56:44.497 --> 01:56:46.931
You're all I have.
You're all I want to have.

01:56:54.941 --> 01:56:56.841
My sweet boy.

01:59:03.703 --> 01:59:06.228
You just gonna stand there
like a bump on a log?

01:59:10.543 --> 01:59:12.010
Go on.

01:59:16.615 --> 01:59:18.082
Come on.

02:00:17.843 --> 02:00:20.471
<i>The only way to be happy
is to love.</i>

02:00:24.850 --> 02:00:26.681
<i>Unless you love...</i>

02:00:28.687 --> 02:00:30.655
<i>your life will flash by.</i>

02:00:41.867 --> 02:00:43.835
<i>Do good to them.</i>

02:00:48.641 --> 02:00:50.074
<i>Wonder.</i>

02:00:54.880 --> 02:00:56.347
<i>Hope.</i>

02:01:48.501 --> 02:01:50.332
<i>Brother.</i>

02:02:40.519 --> 02:02:42.783
<i>Keep us...</i>

02:02:50.362 --> 02:02:52.057
<i>guide us...</i>

02:03:01.640 --> 02:03:03.870
<i>till the end of time.</i>

02:03:46.518 --> 02:03:48.418
<i>Follow me.</i>

02:10:53.278 --> 02:10:54.939
